           Services and Grants for Historical Records Repositories

     * Search for NYS Historical Manuscripts in the RLIN AMC File

     * About the NYS Documentary Heritage Program (DHP)

     * Documentary Heritage Grants Program -- Provides support for
       archives and records-related activities in not-for-profit archives,
       libraries, historical societies, and similar institutions within
       New York State, and from consortia or cooperating groups of such
       agencies.
       The Documentary Heritage Program will also consider supporting
       projects that will be carried out by service providers such as
       historical service agencies, colleges and universities,
       professional associations, or other not-for-profit institutions or
       systems that provide services to historical records programs.

